column2: SELECT DISTINCT po.objid AS phot_id, IS# (pz.z, #) AS phot_z, IS# (pz.zerr, #) AS phot_zerr, po.type AS phot_type, po.ndetect AS phot_ndet, po.clean AS phot_clean, IS# (sp.specobjid, #) AS spec_id, IS# (sp.ra, #) AS spec_ra, IS# (sp.dec, #) AS spec_dec, IS# (sp.z, #) AS spec_z, IS# (sp.zerr, #) AS spec_zerr, IS# (sp.class, #) AS spec_class, IS# (sp.instrument, #) AS spec_inst, IS# (sp.zwarning, #) AS spec_zwarning, IS# (sp.snmedian, #) AS spec_snmedian, IS# (pl.platequality, #) AS spec_platequality, po.modelmag_u AS modmag_u, po.modelmagerr_u AS moderr_u, po.fibermag_u AS fib3mag_u, po.fiber2mag_u AS fib2mag_u, po.extinction_u AS extinct_u, po.modelmag_g AS modmag_g, po.modelmagerr_g AS moderr_g, po.fibermag_g AS fib3mag_g, po.fiber2mag_g AS fib2mag_g, po.extinction_g AS extinct_g, po.modelmag_r AS modmag_r, po.modelmagerr_r AS moderr_r, po.fibermag_r AS fib3mag_r, po.fiber2mag_r AS fib2mag_r, po.extinction_r AS extinct_r, po.modelmag_i AS modmag_i, po.modelmagerr_i AS moderr_i, po.fibermag_i AS fib3mag_i, po.fiber2mag_i AS fib2mag_i, po.extinction_i AS extinct_i, po.modelmag_z AS modmag_z, po.modelmagerr_z AS moderr_z, po.fibermag_z AS fib3mag_z, po.fiber2mag_z AS fib2mag_z, po.extinction_z AS extinct_z, IS# (mp.ptsKey, #) AS tmass_ptskey, IS# (mp.ra, #) AS tmass_ra, IS# (mp.dec, #) AS tmass_dec, IS# (mp.errMaj, #) AS tmass_errmaj, IS# (mp.errMin, #) AS tmass_errmin, IS# (mp.j, #) AS tmass_mag_j, IS# (mp.jIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_j, IS# (mp.nDetectJ, #) AS tmass_ndet_j, IS# (mp.h, #) AS tmass_mag_h, IS# (mp.hIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_h, IS# (mp.nDetectH, #) AS tmass_ndet_h, IS# (mp.k, #) AS tmass_mag_k, IS# (mp.kIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_k, IS# (mp.nDetectK, #) AS tmass_ndet_k, IS# (mp.phqual, #) AS tmass_quality, IS# (mp.ccFlag, #) AS tmass_ccflag, IS# (mp.galContam, #) AS tmass_galcont, IS# (mx.ext_key, #) AS tmass_extkey, IS# (mx.j_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_j, IS# (mx.j_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_j, IS# (mx.h_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_h, IS# (mx.h_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_h, IS# (mx.k_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_k, IS# (mx.k_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_k INTO MyDB.XMC_full_SDSS_data FROM MyDB.XMC_full_SDSS_objid tmp INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid = tmp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objid = po.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj sp ON sp.bestobjid = po.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN PlateX pl ON pl.plateid = sp.plateid LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMass mp ON mp.objid = po.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC mx ON mx.objid = po.objid ORDER BY phot_id
